.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: bellflower, sunflower, dahlia, amaryllis, azalea
There are 5 different nationalities: english, spanish, ukranian, norwegian, japanese
The people have 5 different hobbies: puzzles, card-games, hiking, fishing, collecting
There are 5 different favourite beverages: coffee, tea, milk, orange-juice, water
The people use 5 different means of transport: roller, car, subway, ship, van

1. the english is the person who growsbellflower
2. the spanish is the person driving the roller
3. the person drinking coffee is the person who growssunflower
4. the ukranian is the person drinking tea
5. the person who growssunflower is to the right of the person who growsdahlia
6. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the person driving the van
7. the person who's hobby is card-games is the person who growsamaryllis
8. the person drinking milk is in the middle
9. the norwegian is on the far left
10. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left or right of the person driving the car
11. the person who's hobby is card-games is to the left or right of the person driving the ship
12. the person who's hobby is fishing is the person drinking orange-juice
13. the japanese is the person who's hobby is collecting
14. the norwegian is to the left or right of the person who growsazalea

.:: Answer ::.
